<b>¡MATOI TECH!</b>

117
00:13:22,370 --> 00:13:27,080
<b><i>¡Te extiguiré 
con mi ardiente Espíritu!</i></b>

118
00:13:27,120 --> 00:13:28,000
<b>Clic.</b>

119
00:13:30,170 --> 00:13:33,090
<b>¡Admirad!
Matoi encarna la herencia</b>

120
00:13:33,130 --> 00:13:36,130
