787
01:02:52,300 --> 01:02:53,210
<b>Venga... </b>

788
01:02:54,840 --> 01:02:56,800
<b>¡Bastardo Burnish!</b>

789
01:03:07,400 --> 01:03:10,520
<b>¡QUEMA!</b>

790
01:03:12,530 --> 01:03:15,860
<b>¡Galo! ¡Aléjate de eso!</b>

791
01:03:16,950 --> 01:03:20,700
<b>¡No hace calor en absoluto!</b>

792
01:03:22,120 --> 01:03:26,800
<b>Tus vengativas llamas no
